Oh, my, I guess you've been making round trips empty-handed for days.

00:01:29.214 --> 00:01:32.301
Heaven knows traveling back and forth to the mainland is no easy feat.

00:01:37.764 --> 00:01:42.144
PUBLIC HEALTH CENTER

00:01:54.281 --> 00:01:56.199
DO NOT APPROACH

